---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import "../../styles/globals.css";
import { Header } from "../../components/Header";
import InnerPageCTA from "../../components/InnerPageCTA.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";

const b = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout
  title="parcelLab Wins Smart Solution Award 2019 - parcelLab"
  description="At the EXCHAiNGE supply chain summit, parcelLab received the Smart Solution Award 2019 from LOGISTIK HEUTE and Strategy&, PwC's strategy consultancy."
>
  <Header client:load />
  <main>
    <!-- Article Header -->
    <section class="section-generous">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1440px] px-6 md:px-12">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px]">
          <a href={`${b}/blog/`} class="group mb-8 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--ink-muted)] transition-colors hover:text-[#3D3AD3]">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="transition-transform group-hover:-translate-x-0.5"><path d="M19 12H5"/><path d="m12 19-7-7 7-7"/></svg>
            Back to blog
          </a>
          <span class="mb-4 inline-block rounded-full bg-[#3D3AD3]/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-[#3D3AD3]">Company News</span>
          <h1 class="text-display text-[var(--ink)]">parcelLab Wins Smart Solution Award 2019</h1>
          <div class="mt-6 flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-[var(--ink-muted)]">
            <span>By <strong class="font-medium text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">parcelLab Team</strong></span>
            <span class="h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--ink-muted)]"></span>
            <time datetime="2020-01-06">January 6, 2020</time>
            <span class="h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--ink-muted)]"></span>
            <span>4 min read</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Article Body -->
    <section class="pb-16 md:pb-24">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px] px-6 md:px-12">
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed text-lg">
          At the supply chain summit "EXCHAiNGE," parcelLab received the "Smart Solution Award 2019" from trade magazine LOGISTIK HEUTE and Strategy&, PwC's strategy consultancy. The award recognizes innovative concepts with the potential to transform traditional supply chain value chains.
        </p>

        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed mt-4">
          The company's solution enables customers to enhance postal checkout experiences through real-time order monitoring and personalized, machine learning-supported shipping communication.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">parcelLab Brings the Buying Process to a Good End</h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          PwC partner Harald Greimer praised the solution's capacity to extend beyond B2C ecommerce into B2B applications, where customer relationships are managed by third parties post-transaction.
        </p>

        <div class="my-10 rounded-2xl bg-[var(--surface-sunken)] p-8">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.1em] text-[var(--ink-muted)]">Industry Recognition</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-lg font-medium text-[var(--ink)]">"parcelLab underlines the thesis that successful solutions focus on the requirements of end customers."</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-[var(--ink-muted)]">-- Dr. Petra Seebauer, Managing Director, EUROEXP</p>
        </div>

        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          Dr. Petra Seebauer, Managing Director of EUROEXP, emphasized how personalization throughout the postal checkout journey creates improved customer experiences across the entire post-purchase lifecycle.
        </p>

        <div class="my-10 rounded-2xl bg-[var(--surface-sunken)] p-8">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.1em] text-[var(--ink-muted)]">From Our CEO</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-lg font-medium text-[var(--ink)]">"We hope that by participating in the Smart Solution Award we were able to highlight the relevance of personalized post-purchase communication and that personalization in online retail will advance even further in the future -- from checkout to shipping to returns."</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-[var(--ink-muted)]">-- Tobias Buxhoidt, Co-founder and CEO, parcelLab</p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">About parcelLab</h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          parcelLab provides white-label postal checkout communication technology for online retailers. The platform delivers shoppers with relevant information post-purchase and during shipping through real-time delivery monitoring, sending individualized notifications via email, SMS, Facebook, or retailer apps.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed mt-4">
          The Munich-based startup, founded in 2014, employs over 50 specialists serving more than 350 international retailers across 38 countries and 25 languages.
        </p>

        <div class="my-12 border-t border-[var(--line)]"></div>

        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          The Smart Solution Award win underscores parcelLab's commitment to transforming the post-purchase experience and driving innovation across supply chain communication. As personalization becomes increasingly critical in online retail, parcelLab continues to lead the way in creating meaningful, branded customer touchpoints from checkout to delivery and beyond.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <InnerPageCTA />
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
